# Gemini AI Chatbot

A simple AI chatbot built using Python and Google Gemini API in Google Colab.

## Features

* Real-time AI responses
* Interactive conversation
* Built with Python
* Uses Google Gemini API

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Google Colab
* Gemini API

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies
2. Add your Gemini API key
3. Run the notebook

## Future Improvements

* Chat memory
* GUI interface
* Voice assistant
* PDF chatbot
